title: tamieko
text: great selection of items and prices can't be beat. they sell the same brand items you can find at sirens (if your in canada) but for much cheaper shoes at sirens can cost from 30-50 on here i found the same ones for 9.99 great deal. it helps to buy cute shoes and a matching outfit all in one place. i only wish they had free shipping over $50 to canada because shipping can get pricey however since the prices are so cheap its still worth it even with the shipping
